<div class="brand-path">
  <div class="why-collabor8 row">
    <div class="copy">
      <h2>Manage All Social Media Collaborations In One Place</h2>
      <p>With Collabor8, you are able to keep all of your collaborations and conversations in 1 app. In the fast-paced digital world we live in, we don’t always have time to sort through emails, texts, web inquiries, DMs, PMs, etc. to find a message from someone. In our app, you can manage collaborations across all communication platforms and never miss anything again.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="image">
      <%= image_tag 'WhyCollabor8-iPhones.png'%>  
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="brand-success-stories">
    <div>
      <h2>Brands</h2>
      <p>If you are like most of the brands we work with, time is money. Collabor8 helps you find and work with new influencers who are ready to work with you. Using the app lets you communicate directly with the influencers and eliminate the middle man. Our platform was designed by guys who run a brand for a living, so it has been tailored to suit your needs.</p>
      <% link_to 'https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/collabor8-connecting-brands-and-influencers/id1046316949?mt=8', target: '_blank' do %>
        <%= image_tag 'badge_appstore-lrg.svg' %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="gold">
