      <p>Thread Wallets</p>
    </div>
    <div class="the-little-bookworm">
      <%= image_tag 'brand/little-bookworm.png' %>
      <p>I'm loving it! No more messing about networking on IG! And the brands approach ME as opposed to vice versa?! It's excellent, thanks so much for what I'm sure was many days (and nights!) work to get this app off the ground.</p>
      <p>Little Bookworm</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rad-swim">
      <%= image_tag 'brand/rad-swim.png' %>
      <p>We love Collabor8!! It's been working really well for us. Thank you!!!</p>
      <p>Rad Swim</p>
    </div>
    <div class="wilcox-boots">
      <%= image_tag 'brand/wilcox-boots.png' %>
