      <p>Wilcox Boots</p>
    </div>
    <div class="arvo">
      <%= image_tag 'brand/arvo.jpg' %>
      <p>Collabor8 has been an integral part of our influencer marketing efforts this past year and has helped us navigate over 200 collaborations! Managing our collaborations within one platform has been a game changer for our small team as we grow. We have recommended this to many other brands and we look forward to what Collabor8 has to offer in upcoming months!</p>
      <p>Arvo</p>
    </div>
    <div class="Cariloha">
      <%= image_tag 'brand/cariloha.png' %>
      <p>Collabor8 has been the perfect app for our business to quickly be connected with influencers at the drop of a hat. Influencer marketing has been so beneficial to us by providing us with networking outside of our own marketing initiatives. Collabor8 is so easy to use and lines you up with influencers that are cohesive with your needs. We saw a huge jump in both revenue and followers and give all credit to Collabor8. I would definitely recommend this app to EVERYBODY.</p>
      <p>Cariloha</p>
